--->>OOP:-
class:-class is like a object 
properties:-it is like the variable we change it also or we can create static value.
method:-it is like somewhat functions.it can be public private protected.
public:-it can be accessed anywhere inside the code.
private:-it can not be accessed anywhere.
protected:-it means it can be accessed in class itself and methods can be accessed.
new:-creates new instance of class.


